    <div class="header">
        <h1>Learn More About Becoming a Property Owner</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Why Become a Property Owner?</h2>
            <p>Owning property can be a rewarding experience. Not only does it provide you with a steady stream of income, but it also allows you to be part of a growing real estate market. Here’s why you should consider becoming a property owner:</p>
            <ul class="benefits-list">
                <li><i class="fas fa-dollar-sign"></i> Steady Rental Income: Benefit from regular rental payments.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Property Appreciation: Watch your investment grow in value over time.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Diversification: Add real estate to your investment portfolio for diversification.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i> Control: Manage and improve your property as you see fit.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>How It Works</h2>
            <p>Getting started is easy. Here’s a brief overview of the process:</p>
            <ol>
                <li><b>Sign Up:</b> Register on our platform and provide some basic information about your property.</li>
                <li><b>List Your Property:</b> Create a detailed listing with photos and descriptions.</li>
                <li><b>Connect with Renters:</b> Our platform will help you connect with potential renters.</li>
                <li><b>Manage Your Property:</b> Use our tools to manage bookings, payments, and property maintenance.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
            <p>If you’re ready to become a property owner and start benefiting from the advantages of real estate, click the button below to get started.</p>
            <a href="/signup" class="cta-button">Get Started</a>
        </div>
